{"tid":1512343,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"香城online LFG","createTime":"2019-08-28T00:30:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T01:05:15.000Z","uid":215950,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b3cab95f2726d82be900aba6b006f3ab228151fd","tid":1512343,"uid":215950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T00:30:52.000Z","msg":"有打開 mmorpg 既都應該知咩係 LFG (Looking For Group)，而家有無數咁多資料證明小隊比雜成更有用處，所以想組隊既不妨向手臂寫 lfg，打香城online 個時方便搵隊友。<br />\n<br />\n至於幾多人一隊好呢？ 一條行車線大概 3米闊，平均 2-3 線計，10人係一個幾平衡既選擇。 再多就難以管理，太少就冇效果。<br />\n<br />\n真心推介大家試下。"},{"pid":"6da782fb2c40b200f3f02fd4d3dbf3942dce5933","tid":1512343,"uid":52817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T00:31:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NSAWdB2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNSAWdB2.jpg&h=7e1fa5a5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e96bea6acbfea7624bfb7b9c6250c2ea4e99d208","tid":1512343,"uid":287028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T00:51:26.000Z","msg":"小隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95dbba1edefba33c5d5e5f0ec108ed2875a91753","tid":1512343,"uid":287028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T00:51:51.000Z","msg":"講下要咩職先啦"},{"pid":"3c541dfe2ed58c05d0e868c08d1607eb78004e47","tid":1512343,"uid":215950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"95dbba1edefba33c5d5e5f0ec108ed2875a91753","tid":1512343,"uid":287028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T00:51:51.000Z","msg":"講下要咩職先啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T00:59:32.000Z","msg":"我個人覺得，成個小隊同一個職能係最好。<br />\n<br />\n例如反速蟲隊，係成隊有盾而家且大大隻跑得快既，平時會匿埋係中排，只有當對面向前衝到中近距離時，先會成隊衝前進行沖散，阻止，反制，最後速徹既作用。<br />\n<br />\n因為有左呢個明確既目的，就唔會有臨危驚惶失控既問題，而且可以吸到最有效既經驗值。"},{"pid":"7163d8f3c578dc7be29fed046ce5ef1e9f933f48","tid":1512343,"uid":287028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c541dfe2ed58c05d0e868c08d1607eb78004e47","tid":1512343,"u